<html lang='es'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Factura Aprobada</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f7fe;
        font-family:
          'DM Sans',
          'Plus Jakarta Sans',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        color: #1b2559;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        background-color: #f4f7fe;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(112, 144, 176, 0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 30px 30px;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1b2559;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 40px;
        color: #1b2559;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #1b2559;
      }
      .details-card {
        background-color: #f4f7fe;
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }
      .details-card ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .details-card li {
        margin: 12px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1b2559;
      }
      .details-card strong {
        color: #4318ff;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .approval-badge {
        background-color: #05cd99;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .approval-badge p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #a3aed0;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        background-color: #f4f7fe;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(163, 174, 208, 0.2);
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #a3aed0;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-wrapper {
          padding: 20px 10px;
        }
        .container {
          border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }
        .header {
          padding: 30px 20px 20px;
        }
        .header img {
          max-width: 140px;
        }
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-wrapper'>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='header'>
          {{#if logoUrl}}
            <img src='{{logoUrl}}' alt='Viatika Logo' />
          {{/if}}
          <h1>Factura Aprobada</h1>
        </div>
        <div class='content'>
          <p>Estimado/a,</p>
          <p>Le informamos que la siguiente factura ha sido aprobada:</p>
          <div class='details-card'>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Proveedor:</strong> {{providerName}}</li>
              <li><strong>Número de Factura:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}</li>
              <li><strong>Fecha:</strong> {{date}}</li>
              <li><strong>Tipo:</strong> {{type}}</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class='approval-badge'>
            <p><strong>Aprobada por:</strong> {{approvedBy}}</p>
            <p>La factura ha sido procesada correctamente.</p>
          </div>
          <p>Esta factura continuará su proceso según los flujos establecidos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='footer'>
          <p>© {{year}} Viatika. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>